text: == Events == * September 23 — Resolution of Investiture Controversy in the Concordat of Worms. * Pierre Abélard writes Sic et Non. * Battle of Beroia == Births == * Eleanor of Aquitaine, Queen of France and England (approximate date) (d. 1204). * Frederick I, Holy Roman Emperor (d. 1190). == Deaths == * Alexander I of Scotland, king of Scots * Ralph d'Escures, archbishop of Canterbury * Ilghazi, Ortoqid ruler of Mardin * Arnulf of Montgomery, Anglo- Norman aristocrat (b. 1068) * Margrave Ottokar II of Styria
